quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,"Day ur twalav ara wid ineûfen l$it n Öebbi, s tijehli? Ssersen agdud nnsen deg uxxam n twa$it"
  14,29,"Loahennama ad ô$en degs: a yir leqôaô"
  14,30,"Gan aS i Öebbi tanudda, iwakken ad telfen seg ubrid iS. Ini: \"zzhut! S tidep, leqôaô nnwen d times"
  14,31,"Ini i imdanen iW iumnen, ad bedden i téallit, ad seddqen seg wayen iten N$at, s tuffra u âinani, uqbel a d ias wass ideg ur illi ssuq, ur telli tdukli"
  14,32,"Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, id Isse$layen aman seg igenni, Issufu$ ed yissen ppemôa, d ôôeéq i kunwi. Inub fellawen s isaffen, u s lbabuô i iteddun di yill, s lameô iS"
  14,33,"Inub fellawen s yiîij d waggur, d imezgiyen. Inub fellawen s yiv akked wass"
  14,34,"Ifka yawen seg wayen akw i S tessutrem. Ma pêesbem l$it n Mass nnwen, ur tessawavem. Ih, amdan, s tidep, d amednus, d ajehli"
  14,35,"Mi inna Ibôahim: \"a Mass iw! Err tamdint agi d tin n laman, Âatq a$, nek d warraw iw, seg wannuz n tâancuôin"
  14,36,"A Mass iw, nitenti, s tidep, telfent aîas n medden. Win iddan yidi, neppa, s tidep, sgi. Win iyi âuûan, Keçç, s tidep, Tepsemmiêev, Tepêunuv"
  14,37,"A Mass nne$! Nek rri$ tanezdu$t, i kra n warraw iw, di te$zut ibuôen, ar Uxxam iK iôqan. A Mass nne$! Iwakken ad bedden i téallit. Err ulawen n kra n medden, ad iêninen $uôsen, £it iten s ppemôat, amar ad snemmren"
  14,38,"A Mass nne$! Keçç, s tidep, Teéôiv ayen neffer akked wayen nenna. Ur iffir wacemma i Öebbi, di tmurt ne$ deg igenni"
  14,39,"Ccekôan i Öebbi iyi d Ifkan, di tewser iw, Ismaâil akked Isêaq. Mass iw, s tidep, Issemêas i tnaâôit"
  14,40,"A Mass iw, Err iyi ad bedde$ i téallit. Akked kra, si tarwa w. A Mass iw, Steôêeb s unuju w"
  14,41,"A Mass nne$! Semmeê ane$, nek d lwaldin iw, akked lmumnin, ass ideg ara d ias uqeîîi"
  14,42,"Ur p$ili ar I$fel Öebbi, $ef wayen xeddmen imednas. Iooa ten kan, ar ass ideg ara beêêren allen"
  14,43,"Ad p$awalen, iqweôôa ff$en d, allen ur ferzent, ulawen d ilmawen"
  14,44,"Nabi imdanen af wass ideg ara ten id yas uâaqeb. Ad inin wid idensen: \"a Mass nne$! Efk ane$ lmudda wezzilen, a d njaweb i unabi K, a neddu d imazanen\". \"Day ur teggulem ara kunwi, zik, ar ur tep$abem"
  14,45,"Tzed$em ixxamen n wid ivuôôen iman nnsen. U Nbeggen awen d amek i sen Nga, u Nefka yawen d imedyaten"
  14,46,"Ni$ undin ccbukat nnsen. Ccbukat nnsen haatent ar Öebbi, xas ma ccbukat nnsen d tid ara isse$lin idurar"
  14,47,"£uôek a p$ilev Öebbi ad Izgel lemâahda S, i imazanen. S tidep, Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô"
  14,48,"Ass ideg tamurt a ppu$al maççi d tamurt; akken igenwan; a d asen ar Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô"
  14,49,"A pwaliv, assen, ibe$wviyen pwaqqnen wa $er wa"
  14,50,"Lebsa nnsen d qevôan, times t$umm udmawen nnsen"
  14,51,"Iwakken ad Ikafi Öebbi yal amdan, $ef wayen ikseb. Öebbi, s tidep, Ip$awal di leêsab"
  14,52,"Wagi d anecced i imdanen, ad pwanedôen yis, ad éôen ar siwa Neppa ay d Öebbi Yiwen, a d mmektin uâqilen"